title: Compensation for victims of uninsured or hit and run drivers

heading_context: Compensation for victims of uninsured or hit and run drivers
chunks.html_content: You may be able to claim compensation from the Motor Insurers’ Bureau (MIB) if you’ve been injured or your property has been damaged because of an uninsured or ‘hit and run’ driver.
chunks.plain_content:
Compensation for victims of uninsured or hit and run drivers
You may be able to claim compensation from the Motor Insurers’ Bureau (MIB) if you’ve been injured or your property has been damaged because of an uninsured or ‘hit and run’ driver.

heading_context: Compensation for victims of uninsured or hit and run drivers
chunks.html_content: Contact the MIB directly or read more information on the MIB website.
chunks.plain_content:

Contact the MIB directly or read more information on the MIB website.
